DESCRIPTION:The largest Caribbean festival in North America\, in its 59th year. Official Launch June 13 at Scarborough Town Centre. Junior King & Queen Showcase July 11. Junior Carnival Parade July 18. OCPA Calypso Showcase July 25. King & Queen Showcase July 30 at Lamport Stadium. OSA Toronto Panorama July 31. Grand Parade August 1 at Exhibition Place/Lakeshore Blvd W. OSA Pan in D Park Aug 2.
